html.body: ONTOX_LL0004_001 Glucose Metabolism Pathways This pathway was constructed based on Wikipathways pathways for Glycolysis and Gluconeogenesis, pentose phosphate pathway, and glycogen metabolism combined and expanded using information from the literature. As a basis, it was used the Metabolic Pathways submap from the Atlas of Inflammation Resolution. All sources were annotated on the edges and are disclaimed below.
